<H3> <TI>   _o_Pronasol Chiapas, National Budget Data </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  94P20364A </F>
<F P=103> 94P20364A </F>
<F P=104></F>



<TEXT>
Article   Type:CSO 

  [Editorial Report] An unattributed report notes that the 
State of Chiapas received the equivalent of 1.590 billion new 
pesos in National Solidarity Program (Pronasol) funding over the 
last five years, representing 6.44 percent of all Pronasol 
disbursements to Mexico's 31 states and the Federal District. An 
earlier report noted Social Development Secretary Carlos Rojas 
Gutierrez's 15 December statement that Pronasol's national 
budget for 1994 would total 8.8 billion new pesos. (LA JORNADA 7 
Jan 94 and 16 Dec 93) 

</TEXT>

