<H3> <TI>   Fujimori To Confirm Bustamante Resignation </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PA1602192194 Lima Radio Programas del Peru Network in 
Spanish 1800 GMT 16 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA1602192194 </F>
<F P=104>  Lima Radio Programas del Peru Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [From the "Newspaper of the Airwaves" newscast] </F>
  [Text] President Alberto Fujimori will confirm in a few 
hours the resignation of Alfonso Bustamante y Bustamante as 
president of the Council of Ministers. Bustamante reportedly 
resigned on 10 February after the government decided to 
promulgate the law on the controversy over jurisdiction. 

</TEXT>

